{"tid":1957736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聯署] 唔想俾啲大陸學生咁易考DSE 就快啲反對取消DSE口試 唔好俾佢開先例","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T14:39:04.000Z","uid":161333,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b2540e32f7faab21f7f738d602a10c9cfa7ef0c","tid":1957736,"uid":161333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"早前政府話因為防疫，要將口試剔除，現任大型補習社的中文科補習導師蔣旻正並不同意教育局的做法。<br />\n<br />\n他認為口試卷對合格邊緣及口試能力較好的考生有重要意義，貿然取消對考生不公平。如果政府係擔心疫情擴散嘅話，應該整份試卷共同進退，不能夠只將口試卷取消。<br />\n<br />\n他亦認為，如果今次取消口試，正正就是一個很好的案例，讓政府日後可以輕易取消口試，以降低廣東話地位。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不論係咪中學生，反對取消口試就入下面條link聯署！</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/DSE_ORALexam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FDSE_ORALexam&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=36a758b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/DSE_ORALexam</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/videos/208073513813746/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fvideos%2F208073513813746%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=2227d4e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/videos/208073513813746/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中英四卷 缺一不可</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eac12e3a5760ed4c379338fdc7d0faf5ae8dbcd","tid":1957736,"uid":161333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8bc62977e2c17cbe2e948963f79ea8aad6510e6a","tid":1957736,"uid":46588,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"DSE一直都可以普通話考中文<br />\n<br />\n關咩事"},{"pid":"ccea45d23e9dbae65344adbd1f97738f03b04dba","tid":1957736,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4